      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and performs reliably, backed by a consistent service record. The brakes feel firm, and the tires have approximately 70% of their life remaining. It has been smoke-free and garage-kept, offering a smooth, quiet ride that feels tight and responsive on the road. This car is ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required.",
